tags: black clover op 13|Grandeur|the dark triad|timeskip black clover|asta|black clover opening 13|crunchyroll|black clover|anime opening|anime op|anime opening analysis|anime op breakdown|asta devil|astaâ€™s mother|astaâ€™s mom|zenon|yuno vs zenon|yami vs Dante|Noelle vs vanica|Noelle|valkyrie armor|mermaid armour|snow man|ãƒ–ãƒ©ãƒƒã‚¯ã‚¯ãƒ­ãƒ¼ãƒãƒ¼|anime trailer|anime|bc|bc op 13|bc op 1
description: This video explains Black Cloverâ€™s OP 13, which is being used for the Spade Kingdom Arc! OP 13 had a lot of imagery that gives callbacks to both previous OPs and the Black Clover manga. OP 13 features the song â€˜Grandeurâ€™ by Snowman.Join this channel to get access to perks and emotes:https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChp-A9cwI6zVcDEuIXO71kQ/joinOTHER VIDEOS:What If Black Clover characters had QUIRKS? - https://youtu.be/Xwc2HPmWMwcYuno's TRAGIC BACKSTORY - https://youtu.be/4wHmXcTObaUBlack Clover OP 13: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aaZq6SXXNt4Art:Astaâ€™s devil + Astaâ€™s mother: https://twitter.com/iluvluvnutellaZeno smiling fanart: https://www.deviantart.com/alanfanartsdh/art/Black-clover-Zenon-VS-Yuno-828742605Lucifero colouring: https://www.reddit.com/r/BlackClover/comments/fjog89/chapter_234_lucifero/Tags:ZenonBlack Clover Op 13BC OP 13black clover opening 13Grandeur Snow ManDark TriadVideo Information:This video breaks down opening 13 for black clover. OP 13 had a J-pop song called â€˜Grandeurâ€™ (by Snowman) which worked really well when paired with the openings visuals.The OP begins with Asta walking through a red hallway with candles surrounding him; this shade of red is the same colour we see when Astaâ€™s devil usually appears. The  only occasion in the manga where candles were on the ground surrounding Asta like this, was when he was about to perform a devil binding ritual, to properly gain control over his anti-magic abilities. This opening scene is a reference to that devil-binding ritual and therefore it makes sense that the red aura of his devil should be illuminating the shot. Additionally, this opening moment is also mirroring black cloverâ€™s OP 1, where we saw a younger Asta walking in the same way, before the scene pauses on his face and has a black and white effect. The same effect can be seen in opening 13 and this intentional parallel is meant to show us how much heâ€™s grown between OP and OP 13.Opening 13 then moves on to Asta flying through the sky on his demon slayer sword, as Finral watches in amazement from the ground. This is a throwback to chapter 232, when Finral couldnâ€™t help but admire Astraâ€™s progress from someone who had no magic and couldnâ€™t even fly on a broom to what he is today.We then get a few cool character shots featuring those who were training in the heart kingdom, such as Luck, Leopold, Noelle, Secre and Mimosa. The scene then switches over to Yuno, who stands on top of the golden dawn staircase. Weâ€™ve seen in the past how usually only the captain or vice captain of the golden dawn stands atop that staircase and during the filler Yuno was promoted to vice captain.After this thereâ€™s a brief shot of this mysterious woman. This moment is a flashback to the past in which Astaâ€™s mother is about to die, and itâ€™s immediately followed by a 1 second clip of a devil possessed Asta going berserk. This scene is interspersed with a glimpse of Yunoâ€™s mother and a flashback image of Zenon from the dark triad, during the night they killed the spade kingdom royal family. We briefly see a present day Yuno screaming in anguish, which was a scene directly from the manga after the golden dawn was just totally wrecked by Zenon.Speaking of the dark triad, they appear immediately after this and it was really interesting to note Zenonâ€™s facial expression here, as he genuinely appears shocked by something. Lucifero then got his own individual moment in this opening because based on everything we know so far he is the strongest devil and the true villain of this arc. Asta is then seen fighting against some nameless spade kingdom goons, before the opening gives us the real thing weâ€™ve been waiting for, which is a preview of the three main fights from the beginning of this arc. Yuno vs zenon looks like itâ€™s gonna be great, Noelle vs Vanica also got some screen time and for Yami vs Dante, we saw Yami in the position to do his death thrust spell.As the opening comes to a close we get a look at the tree of qlipoth which will connect the underworld to the human world and allow the devils to cross over, if the dark triad succeed in their plan.We see the heart kingdom queen falling down in the same manner as in the cover of volume 26, before our boy Nacht makes an appearance.
